Scenario: set up casetype

GivenScenarios: projectsetup.scenario

Given root context
Given subcontext organizations/Organization/organizationalunits/OU1/projects/Project1/casetypes

When command createcasetype with
{"string":"CaseType1"}

Then events createdCaseType,addedCaseType,changedDescription occurred

Scenario: select case-type
Given root context
Given subcontext organizations/Organization/organizationalunits/OU1/projects/Project1/selectedcasetypes

When query possiblecasetypes without parameters
And link command addcasetype with CaseType1

Then events selectedCaseTypeAdded occurred

